<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TimeML><TIMEX3 tid="t0" functionInDocument="CREATION_TIME"/>Twenty-one people were <EVENT eid="e1" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">killed</EVENT> <TIMEX3 tid="t1" type="DATE">late Sunday</TIMEX3> when  two minibus taxis and a truck <EVENT eid="e2" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">collided</EVENT> at Leeuw Gamka, about 400 kilometres  (240 miles), from here on the main road to Johannesburg, police <EVENT eid="e3" class="REPORTING" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">said</EVENT> <TIMEX3 tid="t2" type="DATE">Monday</TIMEX3>.&#13;
A police spokesman, <EVENT eid="e4" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PRESPART" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">describing</EVENT> the accident as "very, very horrific," <EVENT eid="e5" class="REPORTING" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">said</EVENT>  the two taxis <EVENT eid="e6" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">crashed</EVENT> into each other before being <EVENT eid="e7" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PRESPART" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">hit</EVENT> by the truck, which  <EVENT eid="e8" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">dragged</EVENT> one of the minibuses 150 metres (yards) down the road.&#13;
Bodies were <EVENT eid="e9" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">strewn</EVENT> across the road, the spokesman <EVENT eid="e10" class="REPORTING" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">said</EVENT>, <EVENT eid="e11" class="REPORTING" tense="PRESPART" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">adding</EVENT> that seven  people were also <EVENT eid="e12" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">injured</EVENT> in the collision.&#13;
